    "title": "Evaluating the validity of probing attachment loss as a surrogate for tooth mortality in a clinical trial on the elderly.",
    "first_author": "P P Hujoel",
    "corresponding_author": "H A Kiyak",
    "authors": "P P Hujoel, B G Leroux, T A DeRouen, L V Powell, H A Kiyak",
